12:12.949 --> 12:14.472
Mass hysteria.

12:14.516 --> 12:16.953
Illness-like behavior
that quickly spreads

12:16.997 --> 12:18.215
to a whole group.

12:18.259 --> 12:19.695
Even behavior
like singing?

12:19.739 --> 12:23.177
Uh, in 1962, there was
a laughter epidemic in Tanzania.

12:23.220 --> 12:24.744
