to hit Sami?

15:31.321 --> 15:32.844
No!

15:32.888 --> 15:34.846
[laughs]:
Of course not.

15:34.890 --> 15:37.066
Oh, my God.

15:37.110 --> 15:39.199
Look, I-I don't want
to get Lexis in trouble,

15:39.242 --> 15:41.505
but I didn't tell her
to hit anyone.

15:41.549 --> 15:43.855
Are you telling me
Lexis is lying?

15:43.899 --> 15:46.902
No. No, I'm not. I just--
I didn't say anything.

15:46.946 --> 15:48.556
So...

15:51.863 --> 15:53.082
DAVID:
Ben,

15:53.126 --> 15:55.128
