16:53.969 --> 16:55.971
So didn't you call me?

17:01.150 --> 17:03.022
What is this?

17:03.065 --> 17:05.067
Note you left
on my pillow.

17:05.111 --> 17:07.026
[laughs]:
What?

17:07.069 --> 17:08.679
Like a high school crush?

17:08.723 --> 17:11.682
