handwriting it is.

17:23.781 --> 17:25.261
Julia's.

17:26.306 --> 17:27.829
Oh, my God.

17:27.872 --> 17:29.831
You think I would save
one of Julia's notes

17:29.874 --> 17:31.441
to put on your pillow?

17:31.485 --> 17:32.877
How else would it get there?Okay.

17:32.921 --> 17:35.097
