we should

17:39.797 --> 17:41.234
stay apart, but you're
the one who called me.

17:41.277 --> 17:42.887
Renee.What is the other option here?

17:42.931 --> 17:45.629
You thought I was teasing you
with my sister's handwriting?

17:45.673 --> 17:47.544
How does that even make sense?

17:47.588 --> 17:50.199
Okay. I should just go.

17:50.243 --> 17:53.072
David.

17:53.115 --> 17:56.684
David, some people are
not meant for the priesthood.

17:56.727 --> 17:58.729
Take care.

18:05.780 --> 18:06.911
What is this?

18:06.955 --> 18:08.652
The food served here.

18:08.696 --> 18:11.264
Okay, you were right.
There's no asbestos issue.

18:11.307 --> 18:15.616
But the vendor who supplies
your vegetables, DFC Veggies,

18:15.659 --> 18:18.619
