18:18.662 --> 18:19.837
[shushes]

18:19.881 --> 18:21.448
They are
fighting off lawsuits.

18:21.491 --> 18:23.189
And I found traces of

18:23.232 --> 18:24.625
[girls humming
"Pudsy's Christmas"]anhydrous ammonia

18:24.668 --> 18:25.626
on the produce.

18:25.669 --> 18:27.106
It's a pesticide.

18:27.149 --> 18:29.630
It's one of the reasons
that their produce is so cheap.

18:29.673 --> 18:32.807
You think the girls were
affected by the pesticides?

18:32.850 --> 18:33.808
Yes.

18:33.851 --> 18:35.592
What do you need?

18:35.636 --> 18:37.812
Well, we need to question the
girls who were affected again.

18:37.855 --> 18:40.684
Okay. Give me a minute.

18:42.121 --> 18:44.166
My girls aren't
at this school,

18:44.210 --> 18:45.950
yet they're humming
the song, too.

18:45.994 --> 18:46.995
Why is that?

18:47.038 --> 18:48.344
I don't know.

18:48.388 --> 18:49.998
Why do people sing
"It's a Small World"

18:50.041 --> 18:51.869
months after they've gone
through the ride?

18:51.913 --> 18:53.480
It's simple,
it's repetitive.

18:53.523 --> 18:55.351
[girl screaming]

18:55.395 --> 18:56.744
Stop! Stop!

18:56.787 --> 18:59.094
[all screaming]

18:59.138 --> 19:00.400
Stop! Stop!

19:00.443 --> 19:03.664
[screaming continues]

19:03.707 --> 19:04.926
Stop! Stop!Stop!

19:05.883 --> 19:07.320
Stop it!

19:07.363 --> 19:10.366
[girls clamoring, screaming]

19:13.804 --> 19:15.806
[girls sobbing,
clamoring continues]

19:22.509 --> 19:24.206
You told me to hit Sami.

19:24.250 --> 19:25.990
Prove it.
What?

19:26.034 --> 19:27.644
Prove that I told
you to do that.

19:27.688 --> 19:29.907
But you did.

19:29.951 --> 19:32.040
Mm, I think you're mistaking me
with someone else.

19:32.083 --> 19:35.609
