You're lying.

19:35.652 --> 19:38.960
Lexi. Lexi, sweetheart.

19:39.003 --> 19:41.354
Listen to me.

19:41.397 --> 19:43.225
There's snitching
and there's lying.

19:43.269 --> 19:46.489
And snitching
is far worse.

19:46.533 --> 19:48.317
Okay, I'm gonna
tell you something

19:48.361 --> 19:50.798
that you're gonna find
out when you're an adult.

19:50.841 --> 19:54.236
And it's probably
the best Christmas present

19:54.280 --> 19:56.499
I could ever give you.

19:56.543 --> 19:58.501
You ready?

19:59.676 --> 20:02.201
Everybody lies.

20:02.244 --> 20:04.855
Yeah, I lie.

20:04.899 --> 20:08.032
But so does your mom and your
dad and all your teachers.

20:08.076 --> 20:09.817
So next time,

20:09.860 --> 20:15.214
tell them whatever it takes to
keep you and me out of trouble.

20:16.432 --> 20:18.913
And here's the most
important thing:

20:18.956 --> 20:22.308
you never, ever, ever snitch.

20:22.351 --> 20:24.658
You got it?

20:25.963 --> 20:27.922
I love you.[ringtone playing]

20:27.965 --> 20:29.837
Oh, I love you so much.

20:29.880 --> 20:32.056
Ooh. I got
to get this.

20:32.100 --> 20:33.754
Hi. What's going on?

20:33.797 --> 20:35.756
Just finishing up
with a patient here.

20:35.799 --> 20:37.584
I wanted to know whether
I could see you tonight.[muffled grunting]

20:37.627 --> 20:39.020
Yeah, yeah.

20:39.063 --> 20:40.630
I'm just finishing up
with my babysitting duties.

20:40.674 --> 20:41.892
An hour?

20:41.936 --> 20:43.546
Sounds good.

20:43.590 --> 20:45.853
Oh, how did the talk
with the granddaughter go?

20:45.896 --> 20:46.854
Good.

20:46.897 --> 20:48.725
Good. Thanks for the advice.

20:48.769 --> 20:51.511
No problem. Just giving back.
Love you.

20:51.554 --> 20:53.121
Love you, too.

20:56.385 --> 20:57.821
Hi.

21:05.133 --> 21:07.178
Can you hear me, Emma?

21:07.222 --> 21:09.093
Yeah.

21:09.137 --> 21:10.791
Why did you put scissors
in your ear?

21:10.834 --> 21:12.314
The noise.

21:12.358 --> 21:14.142
It just kept getting worse.

21:15.796 --> 21:19.103
Have you ever heard of anything
called "Pudsy's Christmas"?

21:19.147 --> 21:21.018
No.

21:21.062 --> 21:23.238
KRISTEN:
The school's given us
permission to check

21:23.282 --> 21:25.545
your browser history.
Are you okay with that?

21:25.588 --> 21:26.763
Mm-hmm.

21:26.807 --> 21:28.809
Yeah, it's in my bag.

21:30.463 --> 21:32.073
What about school lunches?

21:32.116 --> 21:34.423
Have you been eating
a lot of the salads?

21:34.467 --> 21:36.033
No.

21:36.077 --> 21:38.035
No?

21:38.079 --> 21:40.037
What do you eat
at the cafeteria?

21:40.081 --> 21:41.778
French fries.

21:41.822 --> 21:43.345
That's all you eat,
French fries?

21:43.389 --> 21:45.260
Yeah.Everything else is gross.

21:45.304 --> 21:47.088
Okay.

21:47.131 --> 21:49.308
KRISTEN:
We really need your help

21:49.351 --> 21:50.526
getting to the bottom
of this.

21:53.616 --> 21:56.097
Emma, what is Malindaz?

21:56.140 --> 21:58.099
"Malindaz"?

21:58.142 --> 22:00.231
Influencer, talks about clothes
and makeup and stuff.

22:00.275 --> 22:02.451
