the whole thing

22:31.175 --> 22:34.614
and says "Malindaz Challenge"
three times at the end

22:34.657 --> 22:37.573
will go crazy![man shouts]

22:37.617 --> 22:39.532
No joke, girl,
completely insane.

22:39.575 --> 22:41.011
So don't do it!

22:41.055 --> 22:43.623
Only three people
have ever done it,

22:43.666 --> 22:46.408
and they ended up in Bellevue.

22:46.452 --> 22:48.062
So stop at the two mark...

22:48.105 --> 22:49.411
[opera singing]:
♪ And don't you dare say

22:49.455 --> 22:51.413
♪ "Malindaz Challenge"

22:51.457 --> 22:53.110
[normal voice]:
...three times.

22:53.154 --> 22:55.025
You have been warned.

22:55.069 --> 22:57.245
She's trying to make
the site sound dangerous.

22:57.288 --> 22:58.942
The less their parents
would approve,

22:58.986 --> 23:00.944
the more kids will
want to watch it.

23:00.988 --> 23:03.425
Listen.
Background music.

23:03.469 --> 23:05.558
The shade that might be
best for you...BEN: There it is.

23:05.601 --> 23:07.168
["Pudsy's Christmas" playing]That's it.

23:07.211 --> 23:08.256
That's where they heard it.

23:08.299 --> 23:10.650
If you've got, like, freckles,

23:10.693 --> 23:12.869
you want to kind of
use it sparingly.

23:12.913 --> 23:14.349
Okay, all right.

23:14.393 --> 23:17.352
I will make the sacrifice
and watch the whole thing.

23:17.396 --> 23:18.919
Well, this is
no time for bravery.

23:18.962 --> 23:20.834
I'm gonna let you.Thank you.

23:20.877 --> 23:22.357
Come look for me in Bellevue.

23:22.401 --> 23:23.445
