23:32.759 --> 23:35.326
Merry Christmas, both of you.

23:35.370 --> 23:36.502
[quietly]:
Merry Christmas.

23:39.679 --> 23:41.637
We should've
gotten her something.

23:41.681 --> 23:44.031
[sighs]

23:44.074 --> 23:46.381
Okay, let's do this!["Pudsy's Christmas" playing]

23:46.425 --> 23:48.427
So first, foundation.

23:49.515 --> 23:52.213
