what I always say!

24:03.224 --> 24:06.532
Use what you naturally have.

24:06.575 --> 24:08.621
Whatever distinguishes you.

24:08.664 --> 24:10.971
And maybe for you,
that's freckles,

24:11.014 --> 24:12.625
so make sure we can see them.

24:12.668 --> 24:16.629
I'm not in love with the texture
