24:16.672 --> 24:19.240
but I am all about
some of their colors,

24:19.283 --> 24:22.809
especially when I use it
with my usual foundation.

24:22.852 --> 24:25.202
And that's
liquid foundation, right?

24:25.246 --> 24:28.075
Never Stick-- check it out.

24:28.118 --> 24:30.120
You know me;
I can sometimes be

24:30.164 --> 24:32.471
all about my neutral look.

24:32.514 --> 24:34.037
[Ben chuckles]

24:34.081 --> 24:36.431
And you can go for something
more dramatic, of course,

24:36.475 --> 24:38.085
but remember...

24:38.128 --> 24:39.826
♪ You'll stand out!

24:39.869 --> 24:42.219
[laughs]

24:42.263 --> 24:45.266
Heavier coverage concealer
