30:42.797 --> 30:45.234
You're not doing this?

30:45.278 --> 30:46.888
No!

30:46.932 --> 30:48.890
David...

30:48.934 --> 30:50.631
what's happening?

30:50.674 --> 30:52.241
I don't know.

30:52.285 --> 30:54.069
