30:55.941 --> 30:58.204
I agree.

31:00.336 --> 31:01.511
LYNN:
Mom!

31:01.555 --> 31:04.471
Mom! Mom!

31:04.514 --> 31:07.169
Stop, Lila, stop! Mom![girls shouting]

31:07.213 --> 31:09.563
It's in her ear!
I don't know what to do!Oh, my God!

31:09.606 --> 31:11.391
